Q10. Generate an email-id for all employees and display. Email id is generated as follows first 3 letters of name in lower case + last 2 letters of job in lower case + @knowit.com
	eg name=SMITH   job=CLERK  
	email-id = smirk@knowit.com


mysql> select ename, job, concat(lower(substr(ename, 1,3)), lower(substr(job, -2)),"@actsC-DAC.com" ) from EMP;
