Q11. List all employees having experience greater than 43 years.


mysql> select ename, hiredate, floor((datediff(curdate(),hiredate))/365) "date differecne" from EMP w
here floor((datediff(curdate(), hiredate))/365) > 43;
+--------+------------+-----------------+
| ename  | hiredate   | date differecne |
+--------+------------+-----------------+
| SMITH  | 1980-12-17 |              44 |
| ALLEN  | 1981-02-20 |              44 |
| WARD   | 1981-02-22 |              44 |
| JONES  | 1981-04-02 |              44 |
| BLAKE  | 1981-05-01 |              44 |
| CLARK  | 1981-06-09 |              44 |
| TURNER | 1981-09-08 |              44 |
+--------+------------+-----------------+
7 rows in set (0.00 sec)






