Q12. Increase the salary by 10% in the database for all employees having experience more than 40 years  


mysql> select ename, hiredate, floor(datediff(curdate(),hiredate)/365) "date differecne", sal+(sal*(10/100)) "Increased sal" from EMP where floor((datediff(curdate(), hiredate))/365) > 40;
+--------+------------+-----------------+---------------+
| ename  | hiredate   | date differecne | Increased sal |
+--------+------------+-----------------+---------------+
| SMITH  | 1980-12-17 |              44 |           880 |
| ALLEN  | 1981-02-20 |              44 |          1760 |
| WARD   | 1981-02-22 |              44 |          1375 |
| JONES  | 1981-04-02 |              44 |        3272.5 |
| MARTIN | 1981-09-28 |              43 |          1375 |
| BLAKE  | 1981-05-01 |              44 |          3135 |
| CLARK  | 1981-06-09 |              44 |          2695 |
| SCOTT  | 1982-12-09 |              42 |          3300 |
| KING   | 1981-11-17 |              43 |          5500 |
| TURNER | 1981-09-08 |              44 |          1650 |
| ADAMS  | 1983-01-12 |              42 |          1210 |
| JAMES  | 1981-12-03 |              43 |          1045 |
| FORD   | 1981-12-03 |              43 |          3300 |
| MILLER | 1982-01-23 |              43 |          1430 |
+--------+------------+-----------------+---------------+
