Q14. Display all names. Length of each name should be 10 characters , add required spaces on left side of name, also display job, length of job should be 9 characters add required on the right side of job.


mysql> select ename,length(ename), lpad(ename, 10, " ") "NewName", length(lpad(ename, 10, " ")), job,length(job), rpad(job, 9, " ") "NewJob", length(rpad(job, 9, " "))  from EMP;
