Q15. Display string “Hello” followed by name having first letter of name in capital, followed by ! for all employees  who earned the commission.


mysql> select ename, concat("Hello ", substr(ename,1,1), lower(substr(ename,2)), " !" ) from EMP where comm is not null;
+--------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
| ename  | concat("Hello ", substr(ename,1,1), lower(substr(ename,2)), " !" ) |
+--------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
| ALLEN  | Hello Allen !                                                      |
| WARD   | Hello Ward !                                                       |
| MARTIN | Hello Martin !                                                     |
| TURNER | Hello Turner !                                                     |
+--------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
4 rows in set (0.00 sec)





