Q20. To find max, min and sum of salary for all employees  .


mysql> select max(sal), min(sal), sum(sal) from EMP;
+----------+----------+----------+
| max(sal) | min(sal) | sum(sal) |
+----------+----------+----------+
|     5000 |      800 |    29025 |
+----------+----------+----------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)






