Q21. Display ename,sal for dept 10 with max sal at the top.


mysql> select ename, sal from EMP where deptno=10 ORDER BY sal desc;
+--------+------+
| ename  | sal  |
+--------+------+
| KING   | 5000 |
| CLARK  | 2450 |
| MILLER | 1300 |
+--------+------+
3 rows in set (0.00 sec)







