Q22. Write a query which will display name, department no and date of joining of all employees joined between  January 1, 1981 and March 31, 1983. Sort it based on date of joining (ascending). 


mysql> select ename, deptno, hiredate from EMP where hiredate between '1981-01-01' and '1983-03-31' order by hiredate asc;
+--------+--------+------------+
| ename  | deptno | hiredate   |
