| WARD   |     30 | 1981-02-22 |
| JONES  |     20 | 1981-04-02 |
| BLAKE  |     30 | 1981-05-01 |
| CLARK  |     10 | 1981-06-09 |
| TURNER |     30 | 1981-09-08 |
| MARTIN |     30 | 1981-09-28 |
| KING   |     10 | 1981-11-17 |
| JAMES  |     30 | 1981-12-03 |
| FORD   |     20 | 1981-12-03 |
| MILLER |     10 | 1982-01-23 |
