Q31. List ename, deptno and dname for all employees who have only 5 letters in the name.


mysql> select e.ename, e.deptno, d.dname from EMP e, DEPT d where length(ename)=5 AND e.deptno = d.deptno;
+-------+--------+------------+
| ename | deptno | dname      |
+-------+--------+------------+
| SMITH |     20 | RESEARCH   |
| ALLEN |     30 | SALES      |
| JONES |     20 | RESEARCH   |
| BLAKE |     30 | SALES      |
| CLARK |     10 | ACCOUNTING |
| SCOTT |     20 | RESEARCH   |
| ADAMS |     20 | RESEARCH   |
| JAMES |     30 | SALES      |
+-------+--------+------------+
8 rows in set (0.00 sec)









