Q34. Display ename,deptno,dname,loc,sal,comm and Total sal for all employees working 
	In the dept located at Dallas.
	Total sal = sal+comm


mysql> select e.ename, e.deptno, d.dname, d.loc, e.sal, e.comm, sal+IFNULL(comm,0) "Total sal"  from
EMP e, DEPT d where d.loc = "DALLAS" and d.deptno = e.deptno;
+-------+--------+----------+--------+------+------+-----------+
| ename | deptno | dname    | loc    | sal  | comm | Total sal |
+-------+--------+----------+--------+------+------+-----------+
| SMITH |     20 | RESEARCH | DALLAS |  800 | NULL |       800 |
| JONES |     20 | RESEARCH | DALLAS | 2975 | NULL |      2975 |
| SCOTT |     20 | RESEARCH | DALLAS | 3000 | NULL |      3000 |
| ADAMS |     20 | RESEARCH | DALLAS | 1100 | NULL |      1100 |
| FORD  |     20 | RESEARCH | DALLAS | 3000 | NULL |      3000 |
+-------+--------+----------+--------+------+------+-----------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)






